awards.text: Nominated for 3 Primetime Emmys. Another 1 win & 2 nominations.

fullplot: Based on a true story. Liz Murray is a young girl who is taken care of by her loving, but drug-addicted parents. Liz becomes homeless at 15 and after a tragedy comes upon her, she begins her work to finish high school.
